name: Data fields that are most frequently changed by HR
query:
SELECT 
SUM((SELECT COUNT ("Request Type")
	FILTER (
    	WHERE (EVENT_NAME IN (
        	'Personal Data Updated'))))) 
AS "",
"Request Type"
FROM "defaultview-299" 
WHERE "Request Type" IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY 2
